org.schema.game.client.view.buildhelper

Annotation Type BuildHelperClass


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface BuildHelperClass
    Every class extending a BuildHelper, that the user should be able to select, must annotate this annotation. Important: The class-file has to be present in the package org.schema.game.client.view.buildhelper, otherwise it will not be found.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String name
      The (user-friendly) name of the BuildHelper.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract String name
        The (user-friendly) name of the BuildHelper. Will be displayed in the BuildHelper-selection.
